Miele & Cie. KG Chooses Nokia Oyj's Nokia Lumia

Thursday, 27 Jun 2013 04:03am EDT

Nokia Oyj announced that Miele & Cie. KG, a premium domestic appliances and commercial machinery for laundry care, dishwashing and disinfection, is switching to Nokia Lumia as the smartphone of choice for its global employees. Additionally, Nokia Lumia offers Miele employees the benefits of a modern smartphone, including secure access at no additional cost to Microsoft Office documents, information and contacts. To increase the efficiency of its users and infrastructure, Miele has already equipped all its work stations with Microsoft products.Â 

